WEBVTT

00:00.234 --> 00:02.601
<i>Previously on "Gotham"...</i>

00:02.796 --> 00:05.483
I'm arresting you
for the murder of the boy you blew up

00:05.508 --> 00:06.882
under the Crown Point Bridge.

00:06.914 --> 00:09.282
And how can <i>you</i> help me?

00:09.317 --> 00:12.264
What do you say, pal? Give me a smile.

00:13.801 --> 00:15.400
I'm not who my parents might've

00:15.436 --> 00:17.336
wanted me to be, and I'm okay with that.

00:17.371 --> 00:18.770
I'm not okay with it.

00:18.806 --> 00:20.272
I went to my lawyer and him draw up

00:20.307 --> 00:21.620
emancipation papers.

00:21.709 --> 00:22.841
Alfred, you're fired.

00:22.876 --> 00:24.543
Now get the hell out of my house.

00:24.578 --> 00:26.278
I am in control!

00:26.313 --> 00:27.679
But why would you want that?

00:27.715 --> 00:29.748
We had so much fun when we were me.

00:30.985 --> 00:32.951
Surprise.

00:32.987 --> 00:34.720
I needed the police to turn on Penguin.

00:34.755 --> 00:37.122
So you sent this monster to my city.

00:40.294 --> 00:42.127
I need you at the head of the GCPD.

00:42.162 --> 00:43.695
Let them think you're a hero.

00:43.731 --> 00:45.297
This is Gordon.

00:45.332 --> 00:47.966
I just shot and killed the Pyg.

00:48.002 --> 00:49.101
Ivy?

00:51.171 --> 00:52.971
What happened to you?

00:53.007 --> 00:54.273
I've been reborn.

00:56.844 --> 00:57.876
And I will never

00:57.911 --> 00:59.478
be underestimated or ignored

00:59.513 --> 01:00.612
ever again.

01:00.648 --> 01:03.181
Let's make Gotham our bitch.

01:05.000 --> 01:11.074
