contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:21.570 --> 01:23.236
Can I help you?

01:28.777 --> 01:31.663
You're so beautiful.

01:31.780 --> 01:34.748
Thanks. Now move.

01:37.953 --> 01:39.412
Hey, Dad, let me tell you
what happened at school.

01:39.459 --> 01:40.551
Oh, my God, you're gonna love this.

01:40.576 --> 01:42.021
- Mm-hmm.
- Can I just tell him, please?

01:42.057 --> 01:43.123
Wait, no, can I tell him?

01:43.158 --> 01:44.190
- Just let me tell him.
- Nice score.

01:44.226 --> 01:46.626
Cindy? Who are these...

01:50.932 --> 01:52.929
Well,

01:53.101 --> 01:55.935
what a charming young lady.

01:55.971 --> 01:57.404
She's so beautiful, Mom.

01:57.743 --> 01:59.009
And cool.

01:59.072 --> 02:03.367
So your perfume turns people
into your superfans?

02:03.404 --> 02:05.170
Like all good things, it'll fade.

02:05.213 --> 02:06.212
But until then,

02:06.248 --> 02:07.447
they're mine.

02:08.417 --> 02:09.883
Freeze.

02:24.674 --> 02:26.307
Not bad.

02:26.709 --> 02:28.635
I'll check out the rest of the house.

02:36.912 --> 02:40.079
My friend thinks we're here to rob you,

02:40.115 --> 02:44.017
but I know who you work for,
Roland Charles, PhD.

02:47.656 --> 02:51.925
How you... torture plants

02:51.960 --> 02:54.407
in the name of science.

03:05.807 --> 03:07.273
Do you ever wonder

03:07.309 --> 03:08.608
how those plants feel?

03:11.680 --> 03:15.837
Soon, you'll share more with them...

03:16.159 --> 03:19.894
...than you ever could've imagined.

03:36.499 --> 03:39.171
What did you do to him?

03:39.674 --> 03:41.674
I gave him what he deserves.

